<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  <title>회원가입</title>
</head>
<body>
<div id="signup-container">
  <h2>회원가입</h2>
  <form id="signupForm" method="post" action="/register">
    <label for="newUsername">이름:</label>
    <input type="text" id="newusername" name="username" required>
    <label for="newUsername">아이디:</label>
    <input type="text" id="newId" name="id" required>
    <label for="newPassword">비밀번호:</label>
    <input type="password" id="newPassword" name="password" required>
    <label for="confirmPassword">비밀번호확인:</label>
    <input type="password" id="confirmPassword" name="confirmPassword" required>
    <label for="confirmPassword">이메일:</label>
    <input type="email" id="newEmail" name="Email" required>
    <button type="submit">회원가입</button>
    <p>회원가입을 완료하셨나요? &nbsp; <a href="/index">로그인 화면으로</a></p>
  </form>
</div>

<script src='/javascripts/sign.js'></script>
<script src='/javascripts/background.js'></script>
</body>
</html>